<p><span style="font-size:170%;"><strong>SCP-CN-1580相关作战记录</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="font-size:140%;"><strong>请在30秒内，念出以下文字。</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">我效忠基金会，我信奉光明，我不属于破碎之神，我是人类。</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
